William Murphy (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Murphy_(actor) 0 William Murphy was an American actor active from the 1940s through the 1970s. The eccentric actor was a long-time friend of John Wayne and Robert Mitchum and spent many nights together with Elvis Presley and his guys from the Memphis Mafia and regarded Hollywood as an open invitation to party all night long.
